title: Embarrassed
lyrics:
I'm embarrassed to know you at all
It's why I keep the conversations small
Is there a reason why you stick around?
And I'm embarrassed when you make a sound
There is a time I hear your voice

When I can [?]



I'm too careless to ignore you

Or is it because you tell me the truth?

So I'll answer whenever you call

But I'm embarrassed to know you at all



The times I bear to hear your sound

I'll admit that your voice is really mine
